cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper proposes a novel operation for creating computationally efficient neural networks, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves hierarchical fusion of feature maps, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The experimental results are conducted on the CIFAR dataset, which is a common benchmark for computer vision tasks (cs.MM).
